original: Eriksson, Gunnar Ture Albert, ingenjör, Karlskrona, f. 4/10/17 i Säbrå föris., Väsiteirnorril. 1., aiv byggm. Albert E. o. 0’liga Dahlberg. G. 44 m. Maj-Brith Möller. — Ex. v. tekn. gymn. i Härnösand 40. Andre avd:ing. v. Karlskrona stads byggn :kont. sed. 44.
translated: Eriksson, Gunnar Ture Albert, engineer, Karlskrona, born 4/10/17 in Säbrå föris., Västernorrland. Son of builder Albert E. and Olga Dahlberg. Married in 1944 to Maj-Brith Möller. He graduated from the technical high school in Härnösand in 1940 and worked as a second department engineer at the Karlskrona municipal building office since 1944.
